Recursion :    functional calling itself untill the condition met.

example;     printing the name N times

          printName(String name, int count, int N) {

            if ( count == N ){
                return                --->>  This is base case,  once this pass the  recursion will end.
                      }
            System.out.println(name);

            printName(name,count + 1, N);

           }



