Example 3:     Print sum of n numbers

public int sum(int n){
        if(n == 1){
            return 1;
        }
        
        return n + sum(n-1);  --  this will print the sum of n and previous numbers
        
        
    }



example 4:              Fibonnacci


                    fib(n) = fib(n-1) + fib(n-2)          this is the logic:



           public static int fibonacci(int N) {
        // Base case: return N if it's 0 or 1
        if (N <= 1) {
            return N;
        }

        // Recursive case: calculate previous two terms
        int last = fibonacci(N - 1);    // (N-1)th term
        int slast = fibonacci(N - 2);   // (N-2)th term

        return last + slast;
    }

